{
  "stem": "25639.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as the inmates from the trains would-- or the newly arrived inmates-- would go through that fence, that gate, they went to music very often.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- in the morning, as we marched to work, we listened to beautiful music in the summer of 1944.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the only summer that I spent in Auschwitz-- that summer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'll never forget the cellist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A very thin, fair young woman, hair shaven, as all of us had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She just fell off her little chair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a folding chair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And her instrument was there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] gathering dust.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this hot sun is coming down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there, nobody-- nobody gave a damn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There she was, fainted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She probably was thirsty, hungry, exhausted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "God knows how many hours she must have practiced on top of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- And the SS would come and listen to beautiful music.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know from reading, much later, that they gave concerts to the SS, but I never heard such a concert at Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Another time, I would see another member of the small ensemble, again, the same way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Instrument on the ground, and-- either a violinist or another stringed instrumentalist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So it was really-- they were treated the same way as we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The only difference was that they wore blue skirts and white blouses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was their uniform, a two-piece ensemble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I sometimes think of this as being very strange-- to-- to have fine music of Beethoven, Brahms-- you name them-- play in Auschwitz-Birkenau, in a death factory.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there-- there was.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
